Localization.Name: Argo Astronautics
Localization.Description: This commercial ship manufacturer focuses on building shuttles, transport vessels and utility vehicles that can be seen around the universe.

Localization.Name: GEO Resource Pod
Localization.Description: Capacity: 10 cSCU\n\nLightweight yet durable, the GEO Resource Pod was constructed to extend the function of your ATLS by providing additional storage for mined ores as well as a convenient way to transport resources to their final destination.
